long_desc.thetext:
Your package vinagre failed to build from source in current rawhide.
https://koji.fedoraproject.org/koji/taskinfo?taskID=17791819
For details on mass rebuild see https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_26_Mass_Rebuild

vinagre is not compatible with the October 2016 API/ABI changes in freerdp. It needs to be updated in order to compile, and such changes backported to at least F25 to fix the various RDP bugs reported here.
Remmina has been compatible with these snapshots of FreeRDP since 1.2-rcgit.17.
This bug appears to have been reported against 'rawhide' during the Fedora 26 development cycle. Changing version to '26'.
Fixed in latest build for both Fedora 26 and rawhide.
